item.title: Do u want a cool pk runescape name? skiller? or main? Here it is
item.dc:creator: @rsc rsc
item.description:
@rsc wrote:

okay, no-one else knows about this so hear it goes:

as your name type:

m qd yourname

replace yourname with a name of your choice.

The space between the m and the q makes it look liek this in rs2:

M Qd Yourname

if you look quickly it looks like m od.

happy i could help, but whatever you do don’t make jagex stop these or use them to scam people.

thanks,
rsc
